title: Behind the Scenes Minis: Immigration Law and Bridges
itunes:title: Behind the Scenes Minis: Immigration Law and Bridges
description:
Tracy and Holly discuss the difficulty in researching the life of Chae Chan Ping, and exclusionary immigration legislation in U.S. history. Talk also covers the lore around the Tacoma Narrows bridge wreckage and the anxiety of driving over bridges.
